{"tid":501978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【十個趣】David Webb：我宣布推出WebbCoin","createTime":"2017-12-17T12:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T14:12:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":96,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"a04af7fb1533858dee37c588f28b11e8ab756d7e","tid":501978,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171217/57593304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171217%2F57593304&d=rgQ2oB%2B6oMbIQfighRH3gosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=8a8fb6d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171217%2F57593304&h=a465befe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171217/57593304</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171217/large/1513503196_345a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171217%2Flarge%2F1513503196_345a.png&h=53e8ca24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n股壇長毛David Webb繼早前撰文批評比特幣（Bitcoin）是全球首個分散式龐氏騙局後，今日於其網站又有「抽水」新作，稱計畫推出WebbCoin。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb指，WebbCoin會透過其網站的「單一權威服務器」WebbChain ledger上運行。由於一切中央化處理，故可以如比特幣般解決雙重支付（Double Spending）問題，並且可以取代比特幣麻煩的採礦機制。<br />\n<br />\nWebbCoin最初將有三個賬戶單位：Webble，Wibble和Wobble。1個Webble等於100個Wibbles，1個Wibble等於100個Wobbles。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb指，他只會發行100萬個Webbles，發行量將較比特幣少21倍。每名用戶於他的網頁上都有一個安全的Webb-Wallet來存放他們的WebbCoin，交易不收手續費，但「平台會賣廣告或大麻」。目前全球黃金總值約為6萬億美元，當WebbCoin取代黃金，每個Webble的價值相當於600萬美元。他會率先向其網頁的24,000名訂閱用戶，每人發放40個Webbles。<br />\n<br />\n適逢聖誕節，他又指，明天開始的1週內，願意以21個比特幣兌換1個WebbCoin，其後將會「加價」至每42個比特幣兌換1個WebbCoin，但建議「大家不要一下子花掉WebbCoin，唔係無得繼續玩」。"},{"pid":"a226b486b5c9af4f7de49251b0d17339692d134a","tid":501978,"uid":65371,"like":7,"dislike":30,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4390d0141a8b4a23b454a751fb5a555fefa6c5f","tid":501978,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"民眾證券（0279）好快會被David Webb追擊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">民眾證券（0279）推芝商所Bitcoin期貨交易</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171217/s00002/e267acc5ddfe2292bbdf79dc8ba7f824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171217%2Fs00002%2Fe267acc5ddfe2292bbdf79dc8ba7f824.jpg&h=be774f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171217/s00002/1513496853367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171217%2Fs00002%2F1513496853367&d=rgQ2oB%2B6oMbIQfighRH3gosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=39cc0681\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171217%2Fs00002%2F1513496853367&h=ad44a057\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171217/s00002/1513496853367</a><br />\n<br />\n民眾金融科技（0279）旗下民眾證券宣佈，繼首推CA核認網上開戶系統後，公司亦將推出芝加哥商業交易所的比特幣（Bitcoin）期貨交易。<br />\n<br />\n芝加哥商業交易所（CME）表示，為回應市場對受監管數位資產市場交易場所日益增長的需求，其決定將在2017年12月18日（美國時間），香港時間即2017年12月18日下午二時，推出基於芝商所CF比特幣參考匯率（BRR）的比特幣期貨，屆時投資者可透過民眾證券買賣該交易所推出的比特幣期貨合約，每張期貨為5個Bitcoin，以比特幣參考匯率(BRR)18000美元計算，每張比特幣期貨合約價值約為9萬美元。"},{"pid":"7ec79ff58f3ab24ba059e7be2ea42b2ec9e89cfb","tid":501978,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢 missed fire<br />\n<br />\n更似IOTA情況"},{"pid":"60ba36a1a330f8378a02d8362d6b231a9bd15380","tid":501978,"uid":104138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171217/57593304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171217%2F57593304&d=rgQ2oB%2B6oMbIQfighRH3gosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=8a8fb6d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171217%2F57593304&h=a465befe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171217/57593304</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171217/large/1513503196_345a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171217%2Flarge%2F1513503196_345a.png&h=53e8ca24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n股壇長毛David Webb繼早前撰文批評比特幣（Bitcoin）是全球首個分散式龐氏騙局後，今日於其網站又有「抽水」新作，稱計畫推出WebbCoin。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb指，WebbCoin會透過其網站的「單一權威服務器」WebbChain ledger上運行。由於一切中央化處理，故可以如比特幣般解決雙重支付（Double Spending）問題，並且可以取代比特幣麻煩的採礦機制。<br />\n<br />\nWebbCoin最初將有三個賬戶單位：Webble，Wibble和Wobble。1個Webble等於100個Wibbles，1個Wibble等於100個Wobbles。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb指，他只會發行100萬個Webbles，發行量將較比特幣少21倍。每名用戶於他的網頁上都有一個安全的Webb-Wallet來存放他們的WebbCoin，交易不收手續費，但「平台會賣廣告或大麻」。目前全球黃金總值約為6萬億美元，當WebbCoin取代黃金，每個Webble的價值相當於600萬美元。他會率先向其網頁的24,000名訂閱用戶，每人發放40個Webbles。<br />\n<br />\n適逢聖誕節，他又指，明天開始的1週內，願意以21個比特幣兌換1個WebbCoin，其後將會「加價」至每42個比特幣兌換1個WebbCoin，但建議「大家不要一下子花掉WebbCoin，唔係無得繼續玩」。</blockquote><br />\nWebble，Wibble和Wobble<br />\n<br />\n好難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54246756611fbaf7e9345995fec1e5495126f7f0","tid":501978,"uid":76705,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T12:23:43.000Z","m