id":"b1fb621d735f25decbaee72c29d1c111152c50b0","tid":501978,"uid":53632,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"人地講下笑啫，咁認真做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942ca5e5a00bdabbc47b0f4af558453873305d7b","tid":501978,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:09:13.000Z","msg":"其實David Webb可以出一個佢認為好有內在價值既WebbCoin<br />\n<br />\n例如WebbCoin無手續費, backed by gold<br />\n<br />\n佢唔好得個講字"},{"pid":"8c3c990b694f55f49400c0fcdb99848c9d221ffa","tid":501978,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地講下笑啫，咁認真做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家都係講下笑<br />\n<br />\nbtw, btc已升到2萬美金<br />\n<br />\n我就真係訓著都識笑"},{"pid":"1e8a4804be8a52cefd194cd51c9fcc273b9ab574","tid":501978,"uid":101392,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撚狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但bitcoin日日升, 似佢被bitcoiner撚緊多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所有泡沫爆破前都係日日升架啦 當年鬱金香狂熱一個鬱金香球可以換到幾層樓 泡沫一爆破即刻變到一文不值"},{"pid":"448b37dbf15f5cf1205492923e60c94c2074bbe2","tid":501978,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撚狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但bitcoin日日升, 似佢被bitcoiner撚緊多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所有泡沫爆破前都係日日升架啦 當年鬱金香狂熱一個鬱金香球可以換到幾層樓 泡沫一爆破即刻變到一文不值</blockquote><br />\n睇完戲？"},{"pid":"89a6d727f90501abaf6911ef8832b5b7aba53809","tid":501978,"uid":49175,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撚狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但bitcoin日日升, 似佢被bitcoiner撚緊多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所有泡沫爆破前都係日日升架啦 當年鬱金香狂熱一個鬱金香球可以換到幾層樓 泡沫一爆破即刻變到一文不值</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/213350_63bbc56d0244779812ea738d62adae99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F213350_63bbc56d0244779812ea738d62adae99.jpg&h=84fb6cb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc5eb8c1b1e47aadcfec16a071c1a03d99f39799","tid":501978,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撚狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但bitcoin日日升, 似佢被bitcoiner撚緊多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所有泡沫爆破前都係日日升架啦 當年鬱金香狂熱一個鬱金香球可以換到幾層樓 泡沫一爆破即刻變到一文不值</blockquote><br />\n睇完戲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呀 啱啱你講先知拍左做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵日睇下先 <br />\n<br />\n本身單嘢喺歷史上都好出名㗎喇 只不過估唔到人類永遠要犯同樣嘅錯誤"},{"pid":"bec605afc70380a7c539418ea32283104613dfea","tid":501978,"uid":34286,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撚狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但bitcoin日日升, 似佢被bitcoiner撚緊多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所有泡沫爆破前都係日日升架啦 當年鬱金香狂熱一個鬱金香球可以換到幾層樓 泡沫一爆破即刻變到一文不值</blockquote><br />\n睇完戲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呀 啱啱你講先知拍左做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵日睇下先 <br />\n<br />\n本身單嘢喺歷史上都好出名㗎喇 只不過估唔到人類永遠要犯同樣嘅錯誤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有經驗的投資者最怕聽到「今次不同」。歷史上太多資產泡沫：17世紀荷蘭鬱金香、18世紀南海泡沫、1980年代日本股市、千禧年科網股泡沫、2008年美國次按等。用「今次不同」來解釋某趨勢時，他們本能地抗拒，認定是自欺欺人。泡沫跟最好謊言一樣，初時必有點根據，最終才變成瘋狂。"},{"pid":"19a9def44465c6f5f1828d61d1382a6758f4e6a6","tid":501978,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"擺明曲緊啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos